// =========================================================================
// Accelerator table — intentionally empty.
//
// All keyboard shortcuts are now dispatched by the keymap system at runtime
// (see src/keymap.cpp + the WM_KEYDOWN handler in src/main.cpp). Each user
// has a regional keymap (USA / FR-CA / FR-FR) shipped in <install>\KeyMaps\,
// and can fully customize it via Tools → Actions (F4).
//
// We keep one harmless entry here because some RC compilers reject an empty
// ACCELERATORS block. VK_F24 is essentially never present on real keyboards.
// =========================================================================
IDA_ACCEL ACCELERATORS
BEGIN
    VK_F24,         IDM_TOOLS_ACTIONS,  VIRTKEY
END

